OL,3,CNew #33M Emergency Department unveiled
OL,4,Cat Swindon hospital
OL,6,FA new #33million Emergency Department
OL,7,Fhas been unveiled at the Great Western
OL,8,FHospital in Swindon - with managers
OL,9,Fpromising a better experience for
OL,10,Fpatients and staff.
OL,12,FThe new facility is 60% larger than
OL,13,Fthe old one, and is designed to cater
OL,14,Ffor a growing population.
