OL,3,CNew #33M Emergency Department unveiled
OL,4,Cat Swindon hospital
OL,6,FIt has 22 'majors' cubicles for
OL,7,Fseriously ill patients, rather than
OL,8,Fthe 15 in the old department. It also
OL,9,Fhas has seven resuscitation bays -
OL,10,Fthere were previously four - and a
OL,11,Fsecluded room for patients in a a
OL,12,Fmental health crisis.
OL,14,F"It's a fantastic environment for
OL,15,Fpatients, but also for staff," says
OL,16,Foperations manager Kevin Clark.
OL,18,F"It's having everything they need
OL,19,Fclose at hand, all the latest
OL,20,Fequipment, everything networked and
OL,21,Fconnected."
