OL,3,CNew #33M Emergency Department unveiled
OL,4,Cat Swindon hospital
OL,6,FWhen the hospital first opened, the
OL,7,FEmergency Department was designed to
OL,8,Fsee around 48,000 patients a year. As
OL,9,Fthe population has grown, the urgent
OL,10,Fand emergency services now see more
OL,11,Fthan 100,000 patients a year. The new
OL,12,Fdepartment is designed to cater for
OL,13,Fdemand up to 2035.
OL,15,FThe new department was due to open to
OL,16,Fpatients on Wednesday 24 July but
OL,17,Fbecause of technical problems its
OL,18,Fopening may be delayed slightly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
