OL,3,CNew #33M Emergency Department unveiled
OL,4,Cat Swindon hospital
OL,6,FAs well as being bigger, the new A&E
OL,7,Faims to treat patients more
OL,8,Fefficiently.
OL,10,FIt is sited next to the Urgent
OL,11,FTreatment Centre - all walk-in
OL,12,Fpatients will arrive there first, with
OL,13,Fstaff deciding who needs to go through
OL,14,Ffor emergency care.
OL,16,FIt has also been designed to give a
OL,17,Fmore comforting feel, with dimmable
OL,18,Flights, glass walls and wood effect
OL,19,Fpanelling.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
