OL,3,CNew #33M Emergency Department unveiled
OL,4,Cat Swindon hospital
OL,6,F"It's trying to make it feel a bit
OL,7,Fmore homely," explains nurse manager
OL,8,FNatalie Lawrence.
OL,10,F"That sense of 'we've got you, you're
OL,11,Fhere'. Reducing that anxiety and
OL,12,Fmaking people feel much more
OL,13,Fcomfortable at a really vulnerable
OL,14,Ftime."
